<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Lal Lenna Jerusalem Thak</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Lal lenna Jerusalem thak chu,
 Pakna gi hawih leh loipna chun a tuom;
 A lopi zie pau tin chengten gen sek mahleu,
 A kimkhat le a gen zo puou.

[V2]
 A kimkhat le a gen zo puou,
 Khawpi hawih sung;
 Lal chungnung pen Lalna,
 A kimkhat kimkhen le a gen zo puou.

[V3]
 2. Mi thiengtho cheng cheng leh Angel vamte,
 Khawpi sung suongmantam hawih chitin chengte;
 Khang thak pilnel zat beih nunga le thak zel ding,
 A kimkhat le a gen zo puou.

[V4]
 3. Namtin, chitin laka simsen lohte,
 Nicheng Belam No Lalna gam a lut ui;
 Thagau tamtak khawpi sung lutte kipahna,
 A kimkhat le a gen zo puou.

[V5]
 4. Guolzo leh hinna Bu a min zikte,
 Di'n Hukdampa chun A ngaihtuoh sak ahi;
 A sepgim nau chawlhsan in Hukdampa vangin,
 A hauhsakna chu chang tan au.</lyrics>
<author>V. Hawla</author>
<hymn_number>215</hymn_number>
</song>